description: Opportunity knocks with this one bedroom + PLUS BONUS office/spare room!! This home is perfect for the investor, owner occupant or first time homebuyer looking to end the rental payment cycle and build equity! This home incorporates a newly installed refrigerator, dishwasher, oven/range and in unit washer/dryer! The bonus room is well sized for a home office, a baby room or extra storage space. Along with a shared outdoor area, ample basement storage, and in unit washer/dryer you have the perfect situation. Wonderful location with T access and all of South Boston's action including the up and coming Washington Village development, do not miss this one!
